Product Requirements Document - E-commerce Mobile App

Overview:
Build a mobile e-commerce application that allows users to browse products, add items to cart, and complete purchases.

User Stories:
1. As a customer, I want to browse product categories so I can find items I'm interested in
2. As a customer, I want to search for specific products by name or category
3. As a customer, I want to add products to my shopping cart
4. As a customer, I want to view my cart and modify quantities
5. As a customer, I want to securely checkout and pay for my items
6. As a customer, I want to track my order status

Functional Requirements:
- User authentication (login/signup)
- Product catalog with categories and search
- Shopping cart functionality
- Secure payment processing
- Order management and tracking
- User profile management

Non-Functional Requirements:
- App should load within 2 seconds
- Support 1000+ concurrent users
- 99.9% uptime
- Mobile-responsive design
- HTTPS encryption for all transactions

Acceptance Criteria:
- Users can complete purchase flow in under 3 minutes
- Payment processing success rate > 99%
- App works on iOS 14+ and Android 10+
- Accessibility compliance (WCAG 2.1 AA)